Stenoscelideini 
<bibRefCitation author="SCHAEFER C. W." box="[641,804,1046,1070]" pageId="1" pageNumber="356" pagination="153 - 199" refId="ref7743" refString="SCHAEFER C. W. 1968: The morphology and higher classification of the Coreoidea (Hemiptera-Heteroptera). Part IV. The Acanthocephala group and the position of Stenoscelidea Westwood (Coreidae). Occasional Papers, University of Connecticut, Biological Science 1: 153 - 199." type="journal article" year="1968">Schaefer, 1968</bibRefCitation>
